---
layout: base.njk
title: Reading
description: Every book I've read, logged by year — with a short note and how I felt about it.
---
<div class="reading-header">
  <span class="reading-eyebrow">Reading</span>
  <h1>Reading Log</h1>
  <p class="reading-intro">Every book I read, kept by year since 2022 — each with a short note and how I felt about it.</p>
</div>

<ul class="year-list">
  {% for y in reading %}
  <li class="year-entry">
    <a href="/reading/{{ y.year }}/">
      <span class="year-num">{{ y.year }}</span>
      <span class="year-count">{{ y.books | length }} book{% if y.books | length != 1 %}s{% endif %}</span>
    </a>
  </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
